{"tid":903562,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"TKO GATEWAY真係一個好好既商場","createTime":"2018-11-15T15:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T16:01:42.000Z","uid":6783,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8637394b94748a95dca0fd63a7cc35c109ff96b8","tid":903562,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T15:48:10.000Z","msg":"大家都知道男人同女仔既去洗手間時間係唔一樣嫁啦<br />\n但就每一個商場男女廁既數目係一樣<br />\n對我地女仔係幾唔公平同方便<br />\n因為有時候多人起上黎真係排15 20分鐘都唔奇囉<br />\n但今日去到TKO GATEWAY之後<br />\n發現原來呢個商場好重視男女平等<br />\n佢係有2個女廁1個男廁同1個無分性別既洗手間<br />\n真心覺得我地女仔受尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YXX8Dcm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYXX8Dcm.png&h=e378457d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf1184f6b3fd9eff87616078681d37cb30c87ccf","tid":903562,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T15:55:38.000Z","msg":"無絲打去過？"},{"pid":"e95332658571df951de503403b0b826b1b0de6e6","tid":903562,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:00:44.000Z","msg":"領展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2900745e05e8ce70b35dc3e4c6a1497dcbe36c","tid":903562,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e95332658571df951de503403b0b826b1b0de6e6","tid":903562,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:00:44.000Z","msg":"領展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:01:12.000Z","msg":"點解要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918435f2a48a064844c2c4ad79c135969080eb54","tid":903562,"uid":68516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c2900745e05e8ce70b35dc3e4c6a1497dcbe36c","tid":903562,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e95332658571df951de503403b0b826b1b0de6e6","tid":903562,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":